# Web Architecture

## Layer Flow

```
routes → modules → components (atoms/molecules/organisms/templates)
                 → services   (promises + hooks + types)
```

## Directory Structure

```
src/
  routes/          → Route definitions only (TanStack Router)
  modules/         → Feature orchestrators (compose components + services)
  components/      → Pure UI (Atomic Design: atoms, molecules, organisms, templates)
  services/        → Data layer (promises, hooks, types — single source of truth)
  i18n/            → Internationalization config + locale files per namespace
  stores/          → Client-only UI state (Zustand)
  utils/           → Shared pure helpers
  hooks/           → Shared custom hooks (non-service)
  test/            → Test setup and utilities
```

## Layer Responsibilities

### `routes/`
- ONLY route definitions (`createFileRoute`)
- Import the module component and wire it to a path
- NEVER contain UI logic or business logic

```tsx
// routes/dashboard.tsx
import { createFileRoute } from '@tanstack/react-router'
import { Dashboard } from '@/modules/Dashboard'

export const Route = createFileRoute('/dashboard')({
  component: Dashboard,
})
```

### `modules/`
- Feature orchestrators — compose UI + data
- Import components from `components/`
- Import hooks/types from `services/`
- Each module follows the standard component file structure
- Modules are the ONLY consumer of service hooks

### `components/`
- Pure UI only — NO data fetching, NO service imports
- Receive data via props (types from `services/`)
- Exception: `useTranslation` is allowed in components (see i18n rule)

### `services/`
- Single source of truth for ALL types and data access
- Types (Response, Request, Payload) are the contracts used everywhere
- Validation schemas (valibot) live in service types (see forms-validation rule)
- See services-layer rule for full structure

## Import Rules

- `routes/` → imports from `modules/` ONLY
- `modules/` → imports from `components/`, `services/`, and `utils/`
- `components/` → imports from other `components/` only (+ `useTranslation` from i18n)
- `services/` → imports from `utils/` and shared `libs/`
- NEVER circular dependencies between layers
